commit.message: chore: price monitor

feat: create onchain orders to sell non-LRC tokens

Changes here:

- BurnManager now has 2 methods: burnLRC & updateTokenPrice
- updateTokenPrice() creates an order to sell fee tokens. The LRC
obtained will be deposited to the BurnManager.
- burnLRC burns all available LRC. That is the FeeHolder LRC & the
BurnManager LRC.

- Orderbook now returns the orderHash on order creation
- Orderbook has a 'cancel' order feature. But it's probably buggy.
